text: Chicwillasaw Creek is a stream in the U.S. state of Mississippi. It is a tributary to Souenlovie Creek. Chicwillasaw is a name derived from the Choctaw language meaning "deserted house". A variant name is "Chukillissa Creek". ==References== Category:Rivers of Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Clarke County, Mississippi Category:Bodies of water of Jasper County, Mississippi
title: Chicwillasaw Creek
